api_list.name: Search Property By Category

required_parameters.name: categoryKey
required_parameters.description:
Search for properties by their category.
`categoryKey` can be retrieved from `api/v1/getCategory`**(Get Category)** endpoint in `Utils` collection as `key` parameter.

optional_parameters.name: minBedrooms
optional_parameters.description: The minimum number of bedrooms required for a property. The range for `minBedrooms` is between 1-8. The **default** is set to **1**.

optional_parameters.name: currency
optional_parameters.description: Search for property in the desired currency. `currency` can be retrieved from `api/v1/getCurrency`**(Get Currency)** endpoint in **Utils** collection as `code`.

optional_parameters.name: nextPageCursor
optional_parameters.description: To access properties on the next page, use `nextPageCursor`. The previous page API call can be used to retrieve `nextPageCursor`. The `nextPageCursor` needs to be excluded if it's the first page.

optional_parameters.name: minBeds
optional_parameters.description: The minimum number of beds required for a property. The range for `minBeds` is between 1-8. The **default** is set to **1**.

optional_parameters.name: selfCheckin
optional_parameters.description:
Self Check-in
0 - False
1 - True
***Note: The default is set to 0.***

optional_parameters.name: priceMin
optional_parameters.description: Minimum Price filter for search.

optional_parameters.name: minBathrooms
optional_parameters.description: The minimum number of bathrooms required for a property. The range for `minBathrooms` is between 1-8. The **default** is set to **1**.

optional_parameters.name: guestFavorite
optional_parameters.description:
Guest Favorite Property
0 - False
1 - True
***Note: The default is set to 0.***

optional_parameters.name: allowsPets
optional_parameters.description:
Allow Pets
0 - False
1 - True
***Note: The default is set to 0.***

optional_parameters.name: flexibleCancellation
optional_parameters.description:
Flexible Cancellation Property
0 - False
1 - True
***Note: The default is set to 0.***

optional_parameters.name: priceMax
optional_parameters.description: Maximum Price filter for search.

optional_parameters.name: instantBook
optional_parameters.description:
Instant Book
0 - False
1 - True
***Note: The default is set to 0.***

optional_parameters.name: hostLanguage
optional_parameters.description: The language that the property owner is familiar with. `hostLanguage` can be retrive from `api/v1/getFilters`**(Get Filters)** endpoint in **Utils** collection as `value` parameter in `hostLanguage` object.

optional_parameters.name: typeOfPlace
optional_parameters.description:
Type of Property

entire_home :- Entire home/apt
private_room :- Private room
